codex
The code paths match the intended shape: G0 now records `missing_reason` and order-independent `retired_twice`, and both analyzers return immediately after populating G0–G7 when G1 is false. One record-level discrepancy has surfaced: both experiment records cite ASM-0625 but neither lists ASM-0626 in `design.n_planned.assumption_ids`; I’ll assess its severity after verifying that the freeze mechanism itself works.
